  "short_description": "Man I Just Wanna Go Home is an \"MSPaint-noir\" visual novel with 13 endings, a unique visual style and a killer 80s inspired soundtrack. The story revolves around a delivery person stranded in an unfamiliar part of the city under the devastating rain. All he wants is to get home. Help him!",
