ragraph\" > \"Choose your own adventure\" gameplay in which every choice matters</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Atmospheric visuals drawn in MS Paint </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > A killer 80s style synth soundtrack.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > A charming roster of characters to meet, to talk to and die with</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > A multilayered puzzle of a narrative  </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > A once-in-a-lifetime opportunity to kick a cop</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Steam capsule by Artyom Trakhanov</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Chinese translation by Cencil</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Japanese translation by Jun Kurihara</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3010070/extras/d80c978f95f810e1ff2b1ae714e662d3.apng?t=1762338011\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3010070/extras/d80c978f95f810e1ff2b1ae714e662d3.poster.avif?t=1762338011\" class=\"bb_img\" width=616 height=347 /></picture></span></p>",
